last_episode_to_air.name: IT BEGINS
last_episode_to_air.overview: A new adventure into Project Ozone begins today! We're beta testing a new version of Project Ozone 3 in Kappa Mode! We've played through Project Ozone 1, Project Ozone 2 Kappa and now we're going to tackle this beast! It all starts from a sapling... how will it end?

name: Project Ozone 3 Kappa Mode by Hypnotizd
original_name: Project Ozone 3 Kappa Mode by Hypnotizd
overview: Project Ozone 3 Kappa Mode! We're playing in Botania's Sky block Garden of Glass mode and we'll walk through everything technical and non technical to get through this pack. Expect lots of automation and all sorts of craziness to happen!
